USB_Audio_SampleFreq_t Struct Reference

24-Bit Audio Frequency Structure. More...

#include <Audio.h>

Data Fields

uint16_t LowWord
uint8_t HighByte

Detailed Description

Type define for a 24bit audio sample frequency structure. GCC does not contain a built in 24bit datatype, this this structure is used to build up the value instead. Fill this structure with the AUDIO_SAMPLE_FREQ() macro.

Field Documentation

Upper 8 bits of the 24-bit value.

uint16_t USB_Audio_SampleFreq_t::LowWord

Low 16 bits of the 24-bit value.
